      <title>巴基斯坦空袭阿富汗东部后八人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/eight-killed-after-pakistan-air-strikes-hit-east-afghanistan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦军方针对阿富汗东部边境地区的空袭造成八人死亡，这一事态发展可能会加剧邻国之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/eight-killed-after-pakistan-air-strikes-hit-east-afghanistan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 08:17:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财政部长阿德耶莫表示他更看好南非</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/us-treasury-is-bullish-on-south-africa-s-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国副财政部长沃利·阿德耶莫表示，尽管南非经济面临诸多挑战，但政府与企业之间的合作正在推动南非的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/us-treasury-is-bullish-on-south-africa-s-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 06:25:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
